                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-40-off218 t18010218-40-cd219"></join>, a pewter pint pot, value 1s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010218-40-victim257" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin 
                     Whitaker
